  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Residence Neige et Soleil are self catered apartments.</p>
<p>Each apartment has a well equipped kitchenette with an oven, microwave and dishwasher. The local shops, bars and restaurants are nearby.</p>
<p>Alternatively, we've partnered up with Huski who provide premium oven ready meals across the French Alps. Huski will deliver your meals directly to your accommodation in time for your arrival, all you'll have to do is cook. If you'd like to know more, please click <a data-udi="umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575" href="/{localLink:umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575}" title="Huski - food &amp; drink delivery service">here</a> for further details.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The spacious apartments are finished to a very high standard, sleeping up to eight people, these apartments are a great option for groups heading to France this winter. . Located in the Grand Plan area of <a data-udi="umb://document/94b0461bf3c0472a89c38df58692ce28" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94b0461bf3c0472a89c38df58692ce28}" title="Les 2 Alpes">Les 2 Alpes</a>, you are just 2 minutes to the slopes, the nearest ski lift and the ski school meeting place.</p>
<h2>Convenient location</h2>
<p>The Residence Neige et Soleil has a fantastic location in the Grand Plan area, just two minutes to the nearest slopes and lifts, making this a great option for those looking to get first and last lifts. </p>
<h2>Alpine apartments</h2>
<p>Each of the apartments is furnished in a modern alpine style, equipped with everything you may need for a comfortable week in the mountains. Offered on a self catered basis, the apartments all have a well equipped kitchenette with an oven, hobs, microwave, fridge, toaster and kettle - so you can whip up tasty meals from the comfort of your apartment. There is a nearby mini-market so you can stock up on the essentials, alternatively there are a good number of restaurants to choose from so you can enjoy a meal out. Sleeping up to eight people, these apartments are a perfect option for a group of friends or families looking for modern accommodation in Les 2 Alpes.</p>
<h2>Relax and unwind</h2>
<p>When you return from a day on the slopes, make the most of the wellness area. Have a dip in the pool and soothe any aches in the jacuzzi area, there is also a sauna and steam room, so you can relax and unwind.</p>]]></description>
