  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One Bedroom with Cabin Apartments</strong> are around 40-60m² sleeping two to six people. These apartments have a double bedroom. living area with a double sofa bed and a cabin bedroom with bunk beds.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom with Cabin Apartments</strong> are around 40-60m² sleeping four to eight people . These apartments have a two bedrooms, a living area with a double sofa bed  and a cabin room with bunk beds. This apartment has two bathrooms and toilets.</p>
<p>The cabin rooms are small rooms which might have an interior rather than exterior window. </p>
<p>Beds are made on arrival and towels and a cleaning kit is included. The apartment should be left clean but an end of stay cleaning is available to book locally (from €59) but this does not include the kitchen.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double beds</li>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Living Area</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Kitchenette equipped with ceramic hob, oven, microwave, fridge, toaster and kettle</li>
<li>Bathroom with shower or bath with showerhead attachment</li>
<li>Ski locker</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
